# Identity Access Management

Features:
Centralized control of your aws account
shared access
granular permissions
Identity fedaration(AD, Facebook, Linkedin etc)
temporary access for users and devices and services
Multi factor authentication
password rotation policy
integrates with aws services

Terms:
Users, groups, roles(assign to aws resources), policies(doc with one or more permissions)
Note:


# ROles
Roles are secure than storing access key on EC2 instances 
Roles are easier to manage
We can attach IAM role to EC2 instance while creating EC2 instalce only
Roles are universal u can use them in any region


